{"tid":1144199,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"追求學妹不成 男大生放話「巨乳同學我要強姦妳」被判刑","createTime":"2019-05-08T03:03:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T03:08:57.000Z","uid":32511,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6915a6dd6bd441d422deb3ee1adf5d485a4b02c0","tid":1144199,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:03:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">屏東</span>魏姓男大迷戀一名身材豐滿的學妹，因追求不成，竟透過網路通訊軟體放話「巨乳同學、我要強姦妳」等帶有恐嚇意味文字，學妹嚇得報警處理，魏姓男大生被依恐嚇罪送辦，法官判他2個月徒刑，可易科罰金及上訴。<br />\n<br />\n魏姓男大生因迷戀同校一名身材姣好的學妹，展開追求，卻遭到女方拒絕，魏男追求不成，竟透過網路通訊軟體持續向該學妹傳遞幾近性騷擾的訊息，去年2月間甚至放話要「強姦妳」，讓被害人飽受驚嚇，遂報警將魏男送辦。<br />\n<br />\n法官認為魏男只因追求女子不成便出言恫嚇，讓被害人心生畏懼，擔心受害，念在魏男無前科紀錄，且犯後坦承犯行，依法判刑2個月。"},{"pid":"ec872702dad67e62e00a96dde722752c468084cb","tid":1144199,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:04:32.000Z","msg":"臭雞勾引毒撚"},{"pid":"05801fac7f125859ec01207688fa1a8e8a1702bf","tid":1144199,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:04:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce7e9549025b8db5f53abfa48d0aae18d51af7a3","tid":1144199,"uid":98399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:05:20.000Z","msg":"圖呢 屌"},{"pid":"cd73cba925c608cb4d1e998acdbf70f1136cbe62","tid":1144199,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:05:50.000Z","msg":"真係強姦可能都係坐2個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10eac27556046dab7ef277fe3b2ab90b6df824f2","tid":1144199,"uid":143260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:06:04.000Z","msg":"You have 10 seconds <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65787e97d45b928410dde94ae48ffd269f323d59","tid":1144199,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:06:46.000Z